snippet.title: Bowser's Fury Online - F3 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a mod for Bowser's Fury that allows you to play with 1-5 (more in the future) players over the internet.
The mod and source code will be available at day of release (03.08.24) at https://github.com/fruityloops1/bf-multiplayer
Join my discord at https://discord.gg/sfSTA9h2UT
